            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> parsley</strong> roughly, including the stalks&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Transfer the <strong>courgettes</strong>&nbsp;from the oven to a plate and set aside&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>feta</strong> to the baking tray&nbsp;and sprinkle it with <strong>sumac</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Place the tray back in the oven<strong>&nbsp;</strong>for&nbsp;6 min</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>",
